            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-08-16 15:54:16" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(literally: hill of Mars) the location of an Athenian court, traditionally associated with a rocky hill close to the Acropolis, though probably located in the marketplace at the foot of the hill</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>Areopagus</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
